[30;1m55 | [0m[35m# The "shellcheck disable" line above the timestamp inhibits complaints[0m
[30;1m56 | [0m[35m# about features and limitations of the classic Bourne shell that were[0m
[30;1m57 | [0m[35m# superseded or lifted in POSIX.  However, this script identifies a wide[0m
[30;1m58 | [0m[35m# variety of pre-POSIX systems that do not have POSIX shells at all, and[0m
